productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
My neighbor Karly has one of these. She works as a gambler and she says it looks tall.
My neighbor Albertina has one of these. She works as a gardener and she says it looks humongous.
